 you can\u2019t help but dance to\n-Easy to learn, fun to play, a challenge to master\n\n(Kon-kon\u2014Nickname for Konpeito, also\u2026What the fox says in Japanese!!)", "short_description": "Premium Features:\n-All Stages and Levels are UNLOCKED!\n-All Future Content Packs are INCLUDED!\n\nImmerse yourself in Gumi no Yume, a virtual dreamworld where you can help Kon-kon and his friends navigate through puzzles full of fluffy marshmallows, jiggly gummies, and much more. It\u2019s a super kawaii candy adventure that brings a new twist to an old puzzle classic."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.iubenda.com/privacy-policy/7759324", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.lucidsight.com/tos.html", "publisher_name": "Lucid Sight, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.lucidsight.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ARCADE", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD", "TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "674371693568232"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12138787_1086330224721258_1576501671_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1cqdnIiYABkQ7kNvgGyJG4h&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDe4SMZo9FppU-NEpGEvfVUmAyIKOZocqbm-0JnHd_MmQ&oe=6718ECFF"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Gumi no Yume - Premium", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_dat